name: The 2nd International Conference on NanoMedicine (NanoMed 2019)
content: The 2nd International Conference on NanoMedicine (NanoMed 2019) will be held from May 29-31, 2019 in Kunming, China. The conference will cover issues on NanoMedicine. It dedicates to creating a stage for exchanging the latest research results and sharing the advanced research methods in related fields.
